title: Pagoda Tree Cornus alternifolia Flower Head 2580px.jpg
description:
DescriptionAPI Photograph of a flower head on the Pagoda Treeen (Cornus alternifolia en ). Photo taken at the Mt. Cuba Center where it was identified.
Camera and Exposure Details:
Camera: Nikon D50
Lens: Sigma 70mm f/2.8 EX DG Macro
Exposure: 70mm (105mm in 35mm equivalent) f/5.6 @ 1/200 s. (200 ISO)
